<br>
As it stands, he is calling fair play with unbalanced abilities exploits under the definition.  Class and PvE balance is Verant's responsibility, and no player is cheating by using the abilities given and intended for her to have.  In contrast, when we talk about &quot;what is exploiting&quot; we really mean &quot;what actions can you take that are cheating, and how do we know that they are cheating?&quot;<br>
<br>
